host_templates._comment:
{FR: Modèle pour superviser les serveurs Linux via SSH}
{EN: Template to check Linux server using SSH protocol}
host_templates.alias: Template to check Linux server using SSH protocol
host_templates.name: OS-Linux-SSH

description.value:
Plugin pack to monitor GNU/Linux operating system using SSH protocol:
* Connections TCP/UDP
* CPU usage
* CPU detailed usage
* Disk I/O
* Inodes
* Load
* Memory
* Ntp
* Packets errors
* Processes
* Quota
* Service systemd
* Swap usage
* Traffic
* Uptime

Plugin Pack pour surveiller les systèmes d\'exploitation GNU/Linux en utilisant le protocole SSH :
* Connections TCP/UDP
* CPU usage
* CPU detailed usage
* Disk I/O
* Inodes
* Load
* Memory
* Ntp
* Packets errors
* Processes
* Quota
* Service systemd
* Swap usage
* Traffic
* Uptime
